# ğŸ”¥ **Deployment Real-Life Example (Easiest)**

**Flipkart app production me chal raha hai:**

| Work                | Deployment Role                |
| ------------------- | ------------------------------ |
| App chalana         | Deployment Pod create karta    |
| Load badhe          | Deployment scale hota          |
| New version release | Deployment image update karega |
| Bug aa jaye         | Deployment rollback karega     |

Deployment = **App ka manager**
ReplicaSet = **App ka team leader**
Pod = **Kaam karne waley worker**

